’Ł@5256c02293f06bc7bcc56e9680ed713d66ebcc0e4a7e33f0922d8a28c8129d92ŁčTitle: title: export const
Path: Examples
Content:
Re-export a constant from another module.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> module spam { export const foo = 3; }
    module eggs { export use spam foo }
    use eggs foo
    foo

3

```
